               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nFor a better understanding of the content of this text, we recommend first studying how to represent numbers on the Soroban and Suanpan abacuses before proceeding (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>).\n\nFurthermore, we recommend studying the text on addition with the *Yupana* Inca, using the *Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay* method by Dhavit Prem, which will be used to aid in understanding abacuses (<htcite3>; <htcite4>; <htcite5>).",
